title: Talkin' 'bout movin'
body: <P>I was talkin to <A title=Davey href="http://www.livejournal.com/users/daveyabe">Davey</A> today about how many different times we've moved...</P><P><FONT color=#ff0000>travis (3:54:39 PM):</FONT> where're you movin?<BR><FONT color=#0000ff>davey (3:54:52 PM):</FONT> across town, cheaper place closer to campus<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>travis (3:55:19 PM):</FONT> cool<BR><FONT color=#0000ff>davey (3:55:37 PM):</FONT> yeah hopefully, fuckin hate movin shit though<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>travis (3:55:58 PM):</FONT> haha, no shit<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>travis (3:56:12 PM):</FONT> i can't wait till i get a damn house<BR><FONT color=#0000ff>davey (3:56:32 PM):</FONT> goddamn for real, find somewhere i want to staaaay<BR><FONT color=#0000ff>davey (3:57:07 PM):</FONT> this is like the 5th apartment in 5-6 years, its insanity<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>travis (3:58:23 PM):</FONT> fuck, i haven't lived in the same place for over a year since my freshman year @ RIT in '97<BR><FONT color=#0000ff>davey (3:58:55 PM):</FONT> lol i made 14 months here<BR><FONT color=#0000ff>davey (3:59:40 PM):</FONT> dick st was damn near a year<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>travis (4:00:08 PM):</FONT> Dorms &gt; Olean &gt; Racquet Hole &gt; UC &gt; Colony &gt; UC &gt; Dickstreet &gt; Greece &gt; Wilmer St &gt; Wilmington St<BR><FONT color=#0000ff>davey (4:00:29 PM):</FONT> goddamn! hahahah<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>travis (4:00:31 PM):</FONT> that's a lot of movin<BR><FONT color=#0000ff>davey (4:00:49 PM):</FONT> racquet hole<BR><FONT color=#0000ff>davey (4:00:50 PM):</FONT> hahha<BR><FONT color=#0000ff>davey (4:02:12 PM):</FONT> jesus i didn't even think of NJ<BR><FONT color=#0000ff>davey (4:02:16 PM):</FONT> forgot i left a semester at dick st<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>travis (4:02:19 PM):</FONT> oh yeah</P><P>Yeah, so basically I've moved a lot:<BR>1997 Olean &gt; Dorms &gt; Olean (summer)&nbsp;&gt; Racquet Hole &gt; UC (summer)&nbsp;&gt; Colony &gt; UC (summer)&nbsp;&gt; Dick St. &gt; Greece &gt; Wilmer St. &gt; Wilmington St. &gt; [NEW HOUSE] 2004</P>
